Olivia Llewellyn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olivia_Llewellyn 0 Olivia Llewellyn (born 1980) is an English actress, best known for her television appearances portraying Isabel Danforth in The Lizzie Borden Chronicles and Mina Harker in Penny Dreadful.
